<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><songwriters><songwriter>Ryan Tedder</songwriter><songwriter>Brent Kutzle</songwriter><songwriter>Tyler Spry</songwriter><songwriter>Steven Mudd</songwriter><songwriter>Josh Varnadore</songwriter></songwriters></iTunesMetadata><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Someday"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="OneRepublic"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Human (Deluxe)"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1873098678"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1502298679"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="USUM72004317"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="003SD4732yq1lf"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="6aDsgHPZsMztSbZernzlF8"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="139994896"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="wjhhm2003"/></metadata></head><body dur="03:03.258"><div begin="00:07.345" end="03:03.258"><p begin="00:07.345" end="00:12.468" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:07.345" end="00:07.620">Some</span><span begin="00:07.620" end="00:07.895">days</span> <span begin="00:07.895" end="00:08.075">I'm</span> <span begin="00:08.075" end="00:08.659">tread</span><span begin="00:08.659" end="00:08.879">ing</span> <span begin="00:08.879" end="00:09.088">the</span> <span begin="00:09.088" end="00:09.596">wa</span><span begin="00:09.596" end="00:09.783">ter</span> <span begin="00:09.783" end="00:09.966">and</span> <span begin="00:09.966" end="00:10.548">feel</span> <span begin="00:10.548" end="00:10.874">like</span> <span begin="00:10.874" end="00:11.098">it's</span> <span begin="00:11.098" end="00:11.575">get</span><span begin="00:11.575" end="00:11.852">ting</span> <span begin="00:11.852" end="00:12.468">deep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有时我努力游上水面呼吸 却感觉自己在沉入更深的水底</span></p><p begin="00:15.357" end="00:20.449" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:15.357" end="00:15.606">Some</span> <span begin="00:15.606" end="00:15.866">nights</span> <span begin="00:15.866" end="00:16.106">I</span> <span begin="00:16.106" end="00:16.636">drown</span> <span begin="00:16.636" end="00:16.830">in</span> <span begin="00:16.830" end="00:17.083">the</span> <span begin="00:17.083" end="00:17.598">weight</span> <span begin="00:17.598" end="00:17.817">of</span> <span begin="00:17.817" end="00:18.085">the</span> <span begin="00:18.085" end="00:18.599">things</span> <span begin="00:18.599" end="00:18.802">that</span> <span begin="00:18.802" end="00:18.956">I</span> <span begin="00:18.956" end="00:19.536">think</span> <span begin="00:19.536" end="00:19.827">I</span> <span begin="00:19.827" end="00:20.449">need</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有时夜深人静 因为我自以为是揽下的一切 层层重担让我窒息</span></p><p begin="00:23.086" end="00:30.628" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:23.086" end="00:23.513">Some</span><span begin="00:23.513" end="00:23.744">times,</span> <span begin="00:23.744" end="00:23.984">I</span> <span begin="00:23.984" end="00:27.160">feel</span> <span begin="00:27.160" end="00:27.461">in</span><span begin="00:27.461" end="00:27.971">com</span><span begin="00:27.971" end="00:28.956">plete,</span> <span begin="00:29.721" end="00:30.628">yeah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有时我觉得自己残缺不全</span></p><p begin="00:31.078" end="00:38.667" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:31.078" end="00:31.233">But</span> <span begin="00:31.233" end="00:31.385">you</span> <span begin="00:31.385" end="00:31.714">al</span><span begin="00:31.714" end="00:32.022">ways</span> <span begin="00:32.022" end="00:35.399">say</span> <span begin="00:35.399" end="00:35.914">to</span> <span begin="00:35.914" end="00:36.949">me,</span> <span begin="00:36.949" end="00:37.422">say</span> <span begin="00:37.422" end="00:37.697">to</span> <span begin="00:37.697" end="00:38.667">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但你总是对我说 对我说</span></p><p begin="00:38.701" end="00:41.263" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:38.701" end="00:39.067">Oh,</span> <span begin="00:39.067" end="00:39.224">you</span> <span begin="00:39.224" end="00:39.748">say</span> <span begin="00:39.748" end="00:40.132">some</span><span begin="00:40.132" end="00:40.307">day</span> <span begin="00:40.307" end="00:40.615">when</span> <span begin="00:40.615" end="00:40.756">we're</span> <span begin="00:40.756" end="00:41.147">old</span><span begin="00:41.147" end="00:41.263">er</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你说 终有一天 等我们年纪更长</span></p><p begin="00:41.263" end="00:43.377" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:41.263" end="00:41.570">We'll</span> <span begin="00:41.570" end="00:41.736">be</span> <span begin="00:41.736" end="00:42.063">shin</span><span begin="00:42.063" end="00:42.289">in'</span> <span begin="00:42.289" end="00:42.522">like</span> <span begin="00:42.522" end="00:42.786">we're</span> <span begin="00:42.786" end="00:43.146">gold,</span> <span begin="00:43.146" end="00:43.377">yeah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们会像金子一般闪闪发光</span></p><p begin="00:43.377" end="00:45.362" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:43.377" end="00:43.875">Won't</span> <span begin="00:43.875" end="00:44.362">we?</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:44.362" end="00:45.362"><span begin="00:44.362" end="00:44.883">(Won't</span> <span begin="00:44.883" end="00:45.362">we?)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不是吗</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不是吗</span></p><p begin="00:45.362" end="00:47.217" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:45.362" end="00:45.849">Won't</span> <span begin="00:45.849" end="00:46.346">we?</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:46.346" end="00:47.217"><span begin="00:46.346" end="00:46.844">(Won't</span> <span begin="00:46.844" end="00:47.217">we?)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不是吗</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不是吗</span></p><p begin="00:47.537" end="00:49.214" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:47.537" end="00:47.738">And</span> <span begin="00:47.738" end="00:47.990">some</span><span begin="00:47.990" end="00:48.179">day</span> <span begin="00:48.179" end="00:48.501">when</span> <span begin="00:48.501" end="00:48.698">we're</span> <span begin="00:48.698" end="00:49.093">old</span><span begin="00:49.093" end="00:49.214">er</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">终有一天 等我们年纪更长</span></p><p begin="00:49.214" end="00:53.136" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:49.214" end="00:49.539">I'll</span> <span begin="00:49.539" end="00:49.742">be</span> <span begin="00:49.742" end="00:50.041">yours,</span> <span begin="00:50.041" end="00:50.218">and</span> <span begin="00:50.218" end="00:50.560">you'll</span> <span begin="00:50.560" end="00:50.701">be</span> <span begin="00:50.701" end="00:51.046">mine,</span> <span begin="00:51.046" end="00:51.298">babe,</span> <span begin="00:51.298" end="00:51.765">hap</span><span begin="00:51.765" end="00:52.305">py</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:52.305" end="00:53.136"><span begin="00:52.305" end="00:52.774">(Hap</span><span begin="00:52.774" end="00:53.136">py)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">开心点</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们会拥有彼此 开心一点</span></p><p begin="00:53.173" end="00:54.396" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:53.173" end="00:53.774">Hap</span><span begin="00:53.774" end="00:54.396">py</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">开心点</span></p><p begin="00:54.548" end="00:57.147" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:54.548" end="00:54.946">Oh,</span> <span begin="00:54.946" end="00:55.186">you</span> <span begin="00:55.186" end="00:55.611">say</span> <span begin="00:55.611" end="00:55.988">some</span><span begin="00:55.988" end="00:56.194">day</span> <span begin="00:56.194" end="00:56.402">when</span> <span begin="00:56.402" end="00:56.602">we're</span> <span begin="00:56.602" end="00:56.929">old</span><span begin="00:56.929" end="00:57.147">er</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你说 终有一天 等我们年纪更长</span></p><p begin="00:57.147" end="01:00.714" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:57.147" end="00:57.370">We</span> <span begin="00:57.370" end="00:57.674">won't</span> <span begin="00:57.674" end="00:57.981">wor</span><span begin="00:57.981" end="00:58.230">ry</span> <span begin="00:58.230" end="00:58.483">'bout</span> <span begin="00:58.483" end="00:58.602">the</span> <span begin="00:58.602" end="00:58.943">things</span> <span begin="00:58.943" end="00:59.207">that</span> <span begin="00:59.207" end="00:59.349">we</span> <span begin="00:59.349" end="00:59.745">don't</span> <span begin="00:59.745" end="01:00.714">need</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们不会再有不必要的担心</span></p><p begin="01:00.975" end="01:02.812" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:00.975" end="01:01.199">We</span> <span begin="01:01.199" end="01:01.584">don't</span> <span begin="01:01.584" end="01:02.812">need</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不必要的</span></p><p begin="01:03.447" end="01:06.901" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:03.447" end="01:03.655">Yeah,</span> <span begin="01:03.655" end="01:03.949">one</span> <span begin="01:03.949" end="01:04.175">day</span> <span begin="01:04.175" end="01:04.423">down</span> <span begin="01:04.423" end="01:04.569">the</span> <span begin="01:04.569" end="01:04.929">line</span> <span begin="01:04.929" end="01:05.058">be</span><span begin="01:05.058" end="01:05.315">fore</span> <span begin="01:05.315" end="01:05.603">we</span> <span begin="01:05.603" end="01:05.867">both</span> <span begin="01:05.867" end="01:06.147">run</span> <span begin="01:06.147" end="01:06.403">out</span> <span begin="01:06.403" end="01:06.643">of</span> <span begin="01:06.643" end="01:06.901">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是啊 终有一天 在我们走到人生的终点之前</span></p><p begin="01:06.928" end="01:08.269" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:06.928" end="01:07.229">You're</span> <span begin="01:07.229" end="01:07.529">gonna</span> <span begin="01:07.529" end="01:08.269">see</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你会看到</span></p><p begin="01:09.376" end="01:12.118" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:09.376" end="01:09.560">That</span> <span begin="01:09.560" end="01:09.782">some</span><span begin="01:09.782" end="01:10.075">day</span> <span begin="01:10.075" end="01:10.293">we'll</span> <span begin="01:10.293" end="01:10.602">be</span> <span begin="01:10.602" end="01:10.825">all</span> <span begin="01:10.825" end="01:11.098">that</span> <span begin="01:11.098" end="01:11.603">we</span> <span begin="01:11.603" end="01:12.118">need</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">终有一天 我们会成为最理想的自己</span></p><p begin="01:17.456" end="01:20.050" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:17.456" end="01:17.693">Some</span><span begin="01:17.693" end="01:17.939">day</span> <span begin="01:17.939" end="01:18.213">we'll</span> <span begin="01:18.213" end="01:18.491">be</span> <span begin="01:18.491" end="01:18.708">all</span> <span begin="01:18.708" end="01:19.003">that</span> <span begin="01:19.003" end="01:19.451">we</span> <span begin="01:19.451" end="01:20.050">need</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">终有一天 我们会成为最理想的自己</span></p><p begin="01:26.749" end="01:28.891" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:26.749" end="01:26.995">I've</span> <span begin="01:26.995" end="01:27.146">been</span> <span begin="01:27.146" end="01:27.491">the</span> <span begin="01:27.491" end="01:27.978">best,</span> <span begin="01:27.978" end="01:28.171">been</span> <span begin="01:28.171" end="01:28.411">the</span> <span begin="01:28.411" end="01:28.891">worst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我有过辉煌 也有过颓靡</span></p><p begin="01:28.891" end="01:34.686" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:28.891" end="01:29.131">Been</span> <span begin="01:29.131" end="01:29.387">a</span> <span begin="01:29.387" end="01:29.851">ghost</span> <span begin="01:29.851" end="01:30.083">in</span> <span begin="01:30.083" end="01:30.355">a</span> <span begin="01:30.355" end="01:30.953">crowd</span><span begin="01:30.953" end="01:31.203">ed</span> <span begin="01:31.203" end="01:31.956">room</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:33.161" end="01:34.686"><span begin="01:33.161" end="01:33.447">(Oh,</span> <span begin="01:33.447" end="01:33.682">yeah-</span><span begin="01:33.682" end="01:33.957">yeah-</span><span begin="01:33.957" end="01:34.192">yeah-</span><span begin="01:34.192" end="01:34.451">yeah-</span><span begin="01:34.451" end="01:34.686">yeah)</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我像是拥挤房间里无人在意的幽灵</span></p><p begin="01:34.706" end="01:42.473" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:34.706" end="01:34.830">I</span> <span begin="01:34.830" end="01:35.161">took</span> <span begin="01:35.161" end="01:35.274">a</span> <span begin="01:35.274" end="01:35.861">chance,</span> <span begin="01:35.861" end="01:36.150">took</span> <span begin="01:36.150" end="01:36.292">a</span> <span begin="01:36.292" end="01:36.843">turn,</span> <span begin="01:36.843" end="01:37.113">took</span> <span begin="01:37.113" end="01:37.367">a</span> <span begin="01:37.367" end="01:37.894">dive,</span> <span begin="01:37.894" end="01:38.143">and</span> <span begin="01:38.143" end="01:38.316">it</span> <span begin="01:38.316" end="01:38.881">led</span> <span begin="01:38.881" end="01:39.139">to</span> <span begin="01:39.139" end="01:40.